Iron Raptor and Tavatron are behind electrecuted bars.

::Zardus::

Zardus looks at Dark One and his team. "Follow me."

He stands up, heading off toward the storage room with the energon while he 
makes a return transmission to Panzertron: "A group formed on this planet. We 
consist of elite warriors, with me in command."
